## Reload .vimrc
:so $MYVIMRC


## Indenting

       | Indent | Unindent |
Normal |   >>   |   <<     |
Insert | Ctrl-T | Ctrl-D   |
Visual |   >    |   <      |

## Windows

Re-adjust window widths to split window evenly:
N Ctrl-W =

## Search and Replace
# For selection/line:
N :s/[search expression]/[replace expression]/[flags]
# For whole file:
N :%s/[search expression]/[replace expression]/[flags]

flags:
	g - global. Replace all instances in document without asking.

## Visual Mode
# To selection current block (innermost curly bracket enclosed block):
N vi}
